Class ReanalysisDatabase

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.ReanalysisDatabase

  • public class ReanalysisDatabase
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is to manage the connection and queries with the database that stores the information of the reanalysis data files.

      • insertReanalysisFile

        public int insertReanalysisFile(java.lang.String fileName,
                                java.lang.String variable,
                                int numInstances,
                                int numGeopoints,
                                java.lang.String timeFrom,
                                java.lang.String timeTo,
                                float latitudeFrom,
                                float latitudeTo,
                                float longitudeFrom,
                                float longitudeTo)
        Inserts a new reanalysis data file in database.
        Parameters:
        fileName - File name.
        variable - Variable name.
        numInstances - Number of instances.
        numGeopoints - Number of geopoints (latitudes x longitudes).
        timeFrom - Time from of data contained in reanalysis data file.
        timeTo - Time to of data contained in reanalysis data file.
        latitudeFrom - Latitude from of data contained in reanalysis data file.
        latitudeTo - Latitude to of data contained in reanalysis data file.
        longitudeFrom - Longitude from of data contained in reanalysis data file.
        longitudeTo - Longitude to of data contained in reanalysis data file.
        Returns:
        ID of the new reanalysis data file inserted in database or -1 in case of error.
